    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metrogether</strong> 是一款火车模拟器，在这里你可以驾驶地铁、接载乘客、与朋友合作，并探索虚构城市的地铁网络。你可以在单人或多人模式中，作为火车司机、调度员或验票员开始你的旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驾驶火车</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控一列地铁，尽量遵守时刻表，在车站间穿梭时接载乘客，体验这沉浸式的地铁模拟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.poster.avif?t=1753804593\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.webm?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.mp4?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索地铁网络</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入体验这个虚构的地铁网络，里面充满了隧道、热闹的车站和隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.poster.avif?t=1753804593\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.webm?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.mp4?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扮演调度员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入调度办公室，设置列车线路，确保列车准时到达目的地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.poster.avif?t=1753804593\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.webm?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.mp4?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扮演验票员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演细心的检票员的角色，确保乘客持有有效车票。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.poster.avif?t=1753804593\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.webm?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.mp4?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友一起游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友或陌生人联手，共同探索地铁网络。一个人可以驾驶列车，另一个人检查车票，或者在同一个世界里承担不同的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.poster.avif?t=1753804593\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.webm?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.mp4?t=1753804593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火车模拟：驾驶具有真实物理效果的列车，遵守速度限制、在车站和信号处停车、接载乘客和检查车票。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界：乘坐火车或步行探索开放世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无失败画面：即使你闯过信号灯或引发事故，也不会出现失败画面。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线多人模式：与众多玩家同时在线游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色选择：从多种角色中选择，扮演合适的角色或选择一个独特的角色，随你决定。</p></li></ul>",
